match.name: Heathen Precision December 2025 NRL22/P.R.O.
match.about: Roll call and safety brief at 0930. Zero from 1000-1015. We will shoot the NRL COF then quickly setup and shoot the P.R.O. stages. Match will take place in Bay 4 which is between the public 100 yard bay and the parking lot.
